# Personal Portfolio Project (HTML + CSS)

## 📌 Project Overview
This is my final portfolio project built using HTML and a little bit of CSS. The purpose of this project is to create a simple, clean, and responsive personal portfolio website that showcases my skills, education, and projects.

---

## 📚 What You Will Learn
In this project, you will learn:

- How to build a personal portfolio website using HTML and CSS
- How to style a webpage using basic CSS
- How to create layouts using divs and sections
- How to design navigation menus
- How to improve visual presentation of a website

---

## 🧪 Features of This Project
- Home section with introduction
- About Me section
- Education details section
- Skills section with simple styling
- Projects showcase section
- Contact section
- Navigation bar for smooth scrolling
- Basic CSS styling for better UI

---

## 🎨 CSS Features Used
- Colors and background styling
- Font styling and text alignment
- Margins and padding
- Borders and simple layout design
- Hover effects on links (basic)
- Section-wise styling for better structure

---

